{"tid":1546811,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"係Lisbon畀人偷左張香港身份證","createTime":"2019-09-06T12:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T18:23:14.000Z","uid":147659,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7e6491969d134b9baeaf8f753f3ebf05bc8b45","tid":1546811,"uid":147659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"唔好吊我唔小心住 <br />\n我亦都知道係我唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於我有排都未返香港（係英國working holiday緊）亦未能及時買到機票係失竊後嘅14日內返港<br />\n<br />\n唔知倫敦嘅中國大使館會唔會幫手搞補領呢？<br />\n<br />\n有無人有相關類似嘅經驗分享下？<br />\n<br />\nSearch哂香港政府啲網<br />\n只係話「僑居海外嘅香港永久性居民」可以係海外大使館搞手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫到唔清唔楚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：已經係Lisbon報左警 有哂police report<br />\n<br />\n旅行嘅朋友 記得將你個袋 <br />\n放！係！心！口！前！面！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e51370740ce4d2c2d878d49de9a1ef1bb6cbabc","tid":1546811,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbec757aa1f9e2fedc683dc62b2ebec29c8b8874","tid":1546811,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"你亦可致電香港入境事務處協助在外香港居民小組的24小時求助熱線(852) 1868尋求協助。入境事務處會就有關辦理證件的事宜提供意見和協助。"},{"pid":"0fef8d4f4998ee7a4dbcd62be75c99cb68c5a080","tid":1546811,"uid":35393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:34:54.000Z","msg":"有無護照? 有護照都返到香港喎"},{"pid":"bf5282d1b415013ffa15d4091ac9a24048d3929d","tid":1546811,"uid":66357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"用passport出境先"},{"pid":"574f27a21254ce891eaee970a8137f8aa39d5a0e","tid":1546811,"uid":9230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"香港駐倫敦經貿辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有入境處人員"},{"pid":"2e373f27bbcc5b688c764f546669227ac1587371","tid":1546811,"uid":147659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbec757aa1f9e2fedc683dc62b2ebec29c8b8874","tid":1546811,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"你亦可致電香港入境事務處協助在外香港居民小組的24小時求助熱線(852) 1868尋求協助。入境事務處會就有關辦理證件的事宜提供意見和協助。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"首先我要一張打到返香港嘅電話卡<br />\n我會返英國做"},{"pid":"08e199815f89966e5e984fa80e9e92a599caec95","tid":1546811,"uid":147659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:48:11.000Z","msg":"多謝大家嘅回答<br />\n我有護照係身<br />\n不過我驚身份證資料畀人盜用<br />\n所以想申請過張新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c6400360deed575b55c891269f02733d089ead","tid":1546811,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou