:48:11.000Z","msg":"多謝大家嘅回答<br />\n我有護照係身<br />\n不過我驚身份證資料畀人盜用<br />\n所以想申請過張新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"新身分證會有咩資料唔同咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"唔會有野唔同左<br />\n張chip記載嘅野應該唔會變<br />\n我估"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:26:11.000Z","msg":"冇野唔同申請過張有咩用<br />\n即係你想搵張紙證明唔見過身分證啫下話<br />\n報失咪得囉"},{"pid":"0d416ace1b68b34c7f48d953490f21d72a6cfb2d","tid":1546811,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b32fb9c39e260b60fa218bee2f42e945f09cea","tid":1546811,"uid":57488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"唔好戇鳩啦好嘛<br />\n唔見咗咪返香港整囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你換證個身份證好碼咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國大使館整到仲得了嘅"},{"pid":"4ca882eaf5d61f13e3a584e10b19d09fade53a49","tid":1546811,"uid":51501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:30:15.000Z","msg":"係澳洲wh跌過個時都仲有成半年<br />\n警都冇報之後完左先返香港搞<br />\n當上星期係香港跌左<br />\n整身份證唔洗報警都整到<br />\n過關佢有問我做咩唔用身分證<br />\n我話pack左係行李唔記得拎返出黎"},{"pid":"af21f3fca821e78915b03fdbd9ee5dc2fea0b416","tid":1546811,"uid":243516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:32:12.000Z","msg":"報完失之後等真係要返香港時先搞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正係外國最重要都係本護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}